        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4155860/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4155860-2.jpg" alt="xfisher" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27095514/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27095514/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4155860/" class=" " title="xfisher">xfisher</a>
                (真正的价值，缘自于人性的关怀。)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27095514">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">《人间词话》
海宁静安先生此篇，非论词，乃论艺术，论哲学。其境界之论，尤为高绝，中国人文的核心精神，即在于此，古今众人穷其一生，孜孜以求，欲达于此，然不自知，却被王氏一语道破矣。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-06-15 09:54</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                《人间词话》<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>海宁静安先生此篇，非论词，乃论艺术，论哲学。其境界之论，尤为高绝，中国人文的核心精神，即在于此，古今众人穷其一生，孜孜以求，欲达于此，然不自知，却被王氏一语道破矣。
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

<a href="https://www.douban.com/accounts/register?reason=collect" class="j a_show_login lnk-sharing lnk-douban-sharing">推荐</a>
</span>
</div>

                  </div>
                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27095514/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2013-06-15 09:54
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  

      
